{"tid":2256658,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首間「晶片大學」成立 師資存疑","createTime":"2020-10-24T13:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T10:38:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"b583b5f011b533df8568383b7c3aaa42d8c62cea","tid":2256658,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201024/HWVJRBZTNZDSRPJ5SOKFVN4OWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201024%2FHWVJRBZTNZDSRPJ5SOKFVN4OWM%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=22e27890\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201024%2FHWVJRBZTNZDSRPJ5SOKFVN4OWM%2F&h=1d1ea38d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201024/HWVJRBZTNZDSRPJ5SOKFVN4OWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n首間「晶片大學」成立 師資存疑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Oo63VbV7nlwy6Xb-DZxJvcX8DeY=/1686x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IB5AJHCDFFAITLBOEROBRDMXRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOo63VbV7nlwy6Xb-DZxJvcX8DeY%3D%2F1686x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIB5AJHCDFFAITLBOEROBRDMXRM.jpg&h=5e148ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■南京集成電路大學被稱為中國首家「晶片大學」。<br />\n<br />\n為突破自製晶片的技術問題，被稱中國首間「晶片大學」的南京集成電路大學前日揭牌成立，即日已招生及開課，重點培育晶片研發人才。不過，中國網民質疑該學校如何教出人才：「(晶片)自己都造不出來，誰教學生？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n按產業發展需要而建<br />\n<br />\n南京集成電路大學現時設五個學院，另設一個科技園，專門扶持科技企業，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。照產業發展需要而建，目的是銜接高校和企業，完成課程後不會授予學位證書，而是獲結業證書。<br />\n<br />\n同時，華為創始人任正非最近密集式訪問上海交通大學、復旦大學、東南大學、南京大學。消息指，任有意透過高校挖掘人才，助力晶片自主，為華為人工智能，計算戰略，晶片自主等鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n《光明日報》"},{"pid":"336caca386135bc415fe83dda00c0b4485ee4f05","tid":2256658,"uid":54502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:53:43.000Z"